cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.GR 

The paper discusses the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) to understand and create visual art, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the role of learning and culture in understanding art, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper touches on the optimization of physical artifacts to evoke real-world objects, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR).
